 scyther5 123RF.comEntrants should read the Sunday Times Life Style Supplement over the next 10 weeks to review the fashion briefs and enter their designs. If an entry is shortlisted, it will be published in subsequent issues for a public vote via SMS. The candidate with the most votes will go forward for a Lisof assessment test, prior to any award. Lisof offers a Diploma Fashion in Media, Degree Fashion in Media and Buying and its newly launched B.Com Degree in Fashion. For more information, go to www.lisof.co.za/myfashioncareer.